assignments.  Then it evalutes <i>test</i>.  If <i>test</i> evaluates to
zero (or to X or Z) then the loop exists.  Otherwise, <i>body</i> is executed,
the @('for_step') is performed, and we loop back to evaluating
<i>test</i>.</p>

